{"tid":2115743,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"悲觀有咩問題？","createTime":"2020-07-19T17:30:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T04:30:31.000Z","uid":320691,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"441c478f961f2a7a87e7f2f25be1a1c619060738","tid":2115743,"uid":320691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T17:30:20.000Z","msg":"總有啲人好似接受唔到呢個世界有人喺悲觀咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />喺咁要人樂觀要人正能量爆棚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似唔俾人地有一刻唔開心一定要人任何時候都充滿正能量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實悲觀又有咩問題？點解一定喺樂觀先喺正確？樂觀悲觀呢啲好多時都喺透過每個人嘅成長環境同經歷而塑造岀嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔喺話改就改<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就算有得變，都唔會可以突然間成個樂觀曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樂觀顧然喺好但點解一定要迫人去樂觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁樣唔喺更令人難堪？點解就唔可以去接受人地而喺要迫人地去改變？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4238afe41d57b2326676c31bf325a4c502ad4b2c","tid":2115743,"uid":58316,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T17:36:33.000Z","msg":"高大靚仔悲觀 多愁善感<br />\n矮毒撚悲觀 有病"},{"pid":"d6217dbbb5c5769bd30679c848bf4d68ae92f86b","tid":2115743,"uid":92299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T17:39:36.000Z","msg":"冇問題，自己ok咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab8fd20b6673c5e9adbcb7e6b2fe46cb013f12f4","tid":2115743,"uid":214581,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T21:18:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"559b584fbabf3bd1c0b83ae08345936972ca516b","tid":2115743,"uid":262497,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"ab8fd20b6673c5e9adbcb7e6b2fe46cb013f12f4","tid":2115743,"uid":214581,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"